    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-02-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-02-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="180" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d180">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Butler</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-02-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 15,
                                    1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Minister Mariscal, in acknowledging advice of death of Minister Gray,
                            expresses profound regret, and asks the legation to convey to my
                            Government and to the bereaved family the sincere sentiments of
                            condolence of President Diaz.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Butler.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
